Description:
On your way you come across a couple arguing with a talking cat about where the boy with the yellow rat has gone.

As you approach they tell you that they are team of monster trainers and that for the small price of 80g, they are willing to train one of your pets.
DescriptionAction: Although they seem to be distracted by other matters, do you want to pay 80g to train one of your pets?
